---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About - 1g of Code">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About 1g of Code</h1>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>We Learn in Public So You Can Too.</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>1g of Code</strong> is a live stream about the magic of building
          things with AI.
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe the barrier to creating software is disappearing. It is
          amazing what you can build today with a little bit of curiosity and
          the right tools.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What Do We Build?</h2>
        <p><strong>Whatever we are curious about.</strong></p>
        <p>
          We use AI to handle the heavy lifting so we can focus on the creative
          parts. We don't follow a rigid script; if a cool question pops up
          halfway through, <strong>we explore it.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="indent">
          <em
            >Check out the <a
              href="https://sss-snake-by-claude.netlify.app/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>simple Snake Game</strong></a
            > we built live on stream (complete with a global leaderboard).</em
          >
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>The Team</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Graham</strong> A Senior Software Engineer. He knows the systems
          and the rules, but <strong
            >isn't afraid to experiment when the old ways don't work.</strong
          > He bridges the gap between a &ldquo;big idea&rdquo; and the technical
          steps to make it happen.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Kipper</strong> The <strong
            >Professional Question Asker.</strong
          > He ensures we never get lost in the jargon. He asks the questions you're
          thinking—poking holes in the logic and learning alongside you as the projects
          evolve.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Join the Chaos!</h2>
        <p>
          We stream the whole process—mistakes, tangents, and breakthroughs
          included.
        </p>
        <p class="cta-wrap">
          <a
            class="cta-twitch"
            href="https://twitch.tv/1gOfCode"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"
              ><path
                d="M11.571 4.714h1.715v5.143H11.57zm4.715 0H18v5.143h-1.714zM6 0L1.714 4.286v15.428h5.143V24l4.286-4.286h3.428L22.286 12V0zm14.571 11.143l-3.428 3.428h-3.429l-3 3v-3H6.857V1.714h13.714Z"
              ></path></svg
            > Follow us on Twitch</a
          >
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-block: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .about-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    line-height: var(--line-height-base);
  }

  .indent {
    margin-inline: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cta-wrap {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-twitch {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
    padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-xl);
    background-color: var(--color-twitch);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition:
      background-color var(--transition-fast),
      transform var(--transition-fast),
      box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .cta-twitch:hover {
    background-color: #7c3aed;
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgb(145 70 255 / 0.4);
  }

  .cta-twitch:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-page {
      padding-block: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
